---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About EdgeShift - Cloud & AI Engineer">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          EdgeShift は、クラウドインフラと AI を活用したソリューションを提供しています。
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Expertise</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>AWS Infrastructure (Lambda, ECS, Step Functions, DynamoDB)</li>
          <li>Infrastructure as Code (Terraform, CloudFormation)</li>
          <li>AI Integration (Claude, OpenAI, LangChain)</li>
          <li>Web Development (React, Next.js, Astro)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Certifications</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>AWS Solutions Architect - Professional</li>
          <li>AWS DevOps Engineer - Professional</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
